{"tid":2510119,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美憂港入境例禁國民離開  WSJ指抗爭港人恐被困 倡效英收容","createTime":"2021-04-30T02:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T03:20:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7b41af1ac4b88777331929cd54acd9aa5ac55d4c","tid":2510119,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:30:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/AEBOOPVLPVAS3DPCM2ROAZC4OU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FAEBOOPVLPVAS3DPCM2ROAZC4OU%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTyYtkWzW%2FBkyQE6eFpzr100%3D&h=f740fdd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210430%2FAEBOOPVLPVAS3DPCM2ROAZC4OU%2F&h=1fcf7415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210430/AEBOOPVLPVAS3DPCM2ROAZC4OU/</a><br />\n<br />\n美憂港入境例禁國民離開 <br />\nWSJ指抗爭港人恐被困 倡效英收容<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港立法會周三通過《入境條例》修訂，賦權入境處長可限制任何人出入境，香港大律師公會等團體先後表達疑慮。美國及英國政府對有關修例亦抱懷疑，美國國務院發言人發表聲明，對有關修例「深切關注」，憂日後香港像中國般任意動用出境禁令、包括針對美國的公民。外媒亦關注事件，指修例將使曾參與反送中運動的港人擔憂被困，促請美國跟隨英國收容香港難民。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：大律師公會：入境處長權力太闊<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人周四發表聲明，對本港《入境條例》修訂表示「深切關注」，「華府對其（條例）內容、潛在用法、缺乏監督及問責性感關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2VlQETxgOnPkqyPJWBLohGmQJrg=/510x169/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SA2XOJMOYRCENCLFAU54WVR7U4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2VlQETxgOnPkqyPJWBLohGmQJrg%3D%2F510x169%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSA2XOJMOYRCENCLFAU54WVR7U4.jpg&h=637cba3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■《華爾街日報》文章指修訂入境例，標誌香港再走下坡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「港失人才是悲劇」<br />\n<br />\n華府長時間以來一直擔心中國在沒有適當法律程序下，任意動用出境禁令，包括針對美國的公民。我們對香港當局未來採納類似的任意措施表達深切關注」。聲明亦促港府履行其承諾，列明新修訂條例只適用於入境航班。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部亦有發簡短聲明，指民眾離開香港的權利是受《基本法》保障，應確實維護。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》（WSJ）編輯部周三發表評論文章，指入境條例修訂將令港府毋須經法院頒令，便可阻止本地居民及外國人登上飛機或船隻離開，標誌香港走下坡另一步。<br />\n<br />\n文章又形容，修例屬去年港版國安法授權警方申請限制受查人士出境的「放大版」，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》文章又指，英國在1月底開始英國國民（海外）（BNO）特別簽證，質疑北京為免港人大舉移民令中方尷尬，因此「為香港裝上門鎖」，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法新社指商界亦受影響<br />\n<br />\n法新社就指《入境條例》修訂後，當局阻止任何人入境或離開香港的過程中毋須法庭批出手令，亦無法上訴，無論是民主派人士、律師或商界都表達憂慮。。。。"},{"pid":"d5b4df2caec26e8de58f772b46577e301110fe09","tid":2510119,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"如果唔係ted Cruz <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fbb0247d4aa33fdba5121bd94334205f8897697","tid":2510119,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:31:38.000Z","msg":"Yes"},{"pid":"2f85249a78bbe73effec7e5c4debc0a9bb472b7e","tid":2510119,"uid":146030,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d5b4df2caec26e8de58f772b46577e301110fe09","tid":2510119,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"如果唔係ted Cruz <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:39:16.000Z","msg":"佢死十次都唔夠"},{"pid":"5812a5888469e57307b8c693a5283954e3dc4769","tid":2510119,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5b4df2caec26e8de58f772b46577e301110fe09","tid":2510119,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"如果唔係ted Cruz <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/threat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a